title: How to Master the BMAT, 3E (2015)[PDF][StormRG]
description:
TITLE/EDITION How to Master the BMAT: Unbeatable Preparation for Success in the BioMedical Admissions Test
By: Christopher See (Author), Chris Tyreman (Author)
Paperback: 304 pages
Publisher: Kogan Page; Third Edition edition (April 28, 2015)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 0749471875
ISBN-13: 978-0749471873
NOTE: This is the standalone ebook and may not include access codes that come packaged with the bound book




With over 400 practice questions and six mock tests, How to Master the BMAT helps readers maximize their BMAT test score. It focuses on core knowledge in six key areas: aptitude and skills; math; physics; chemistry; biology; writing tasks.

At the end of each section, a set of review questions provides the opportunity to identify and improve weak areas before taking the test. Wherever possible, every question comes complete with its revision topics indicated in brackets, useful hints, and expanded answers. This third edition corrects answer errors and includes new sections and updated science information
